<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <link href="~/Content/js/bootstrap/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="~/Content/css/framework-login.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
     
    </style>
    <title>Login</title>
</head>
<body class="signin">
    <div class="signinpanel">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-7">
                <div class="signin-info">
                    <div class="logopanel m-b">
                        <h1>[ H+ ]</h1>
                    </div>
                    <div class="m-b"></div>
                    <h4>欢迎使用 <strong>H+ 后台主题UI框架</strong></h4>
                    <ul class="m-b">
                        <li><i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-right m-r-xs"></i> 优势一</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-right m-r-xs"></i> 优势二</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-right m-r-xs"></i> 优势三</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-right m-r-xs"></i> 优势四</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-right m-r-xs"></i> 优势五</li>
                    </ul>
                    <strong>还没有账号？ <a href="#">立即注册&raquo;</a></strong>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-5">
                <form method="post" action="index.html">
                    @*<h4 class="no-margins">登录：</h4>*@
                    <input type="text" class="form-control uname" placeholder="用户名" />
                    <input type="password" class="form-control pword m-b" placeholder="密码" />
                    <input id="txt_code" class="form-control" maxlength="4" type="text" placeholder="验证码" style="width: 70px; float: left;">
                    <div style="width: 110px; float: left; padding-top: 18px;padding-left: 18px;">
                        <img id="imgcode" class="authcode" src="~/Login/GetAuthCode" width="50" height="25" />            
                        看不清？<a id="switchCode" href="javascript:void();" style="text-decoration: none;">换一张</a>
                    </div>
                    @*<p class="m-t-md">登录到H+后台主题UI框架</p>
                    <a href="">忘记密码了？</a>*@
                    <button class="btn btn-success btn-block">登录</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="signup-footer">
            <div class="pull-left">
                &copy; 2015 All Rights Reserved. H+
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
